The.Vampire.Diaries.S07E04.720p.HDTV.X264-DIMENSION
Aired 29.10.2015

"I Carry Your Heart With Me"

Just as Damon thinks he's gained the upper hand in
his fight against Lily, an unexpected turn of
events leaves him scrambling for a plan B.
Elsewhere, when the fallout of Damon's actions
gains the unwanted attention of Mary Louise and
Nora, Stefan and Caroline are forced to spend the
night distracting the girls at Whitmore College's
Heaven & Hell ball. Finally, after suspecting that
she's up to something, Enzo sets off on a mission
to find out what Valerie is hiding, while a plan
set by Alaric and Bonnie leaves their worlds turned
upside down.

18/Slower
Evolve... or die.
